## Email

In all cases, please remember **not** to send us your password over email, or your account will be disabled.

* [help@ocf.berkeley.edu](mailto:help@ocf.berkeley.edu)

  The most general address -- any questions about OCF accounts, services, and joining staff can be sent here. Your mail will be seen by all OCF staff.

* [security@ocf.berkeley.edu](mailto:security@ocf.berkeley.edu)

  Concerns about computer security, network infrastructure, and abuse of resources (including spam) should be sent here.

* [hostmaster@ocf.berkeley.edu](mailto:hostmaster@ocf.berkeley.edu)

  DNS changes including [[virtual hosting|services/vhost]] requests should be sent here.

## Telephone

Phoning us is not the best way to reach OCF staff. During lab hours, the phone forwards to the ASUC Publications Center.

If you must call us, please make sure to leave your name, OCF username (if known), phone number, and (preferably) an email address.

* 81-OCFSTAFF (816-237-8233)

