DMCA takedown notices must comply with [17 U.S.C. ยง 512(c)(3)](http://www.copyright.gov/title17/92chap5.html#512) and be sent to the [designated agent at UC Berkeley](http://www.copyright.gov/onlinesp/agents/u/univ_ca_berkeley.pdf). We recommend sending a copy of the notice to the OCF directly ([security@ocf.berkeley.edu](mailto:security@ocf.berkeley.edu)) for faster response.
